room_title: Escape room "50’s Roll ‘n’ Ride Diner" by Escape Room Lancaster in Lancaster
room_description:
Hey you chickie babies, cool cats, greasers, and motor-heads, lace up your roller skates and get to the diner! Let's get hip and have a blast... You're invited to the biggest bash of the weekend! 


The wait staff has the music cranked for a pre-opening dance party when some square loses the key to the front door. Customers are arriving in one hour and you need to locate the key and open the door or risk being sentenced to dish-washing duty indefinitely.
